<abstract><t>This document describes a protocol and DNS Resource Record used to provide a message digest over DNS zone data.  In particular, it describes how to compute, sign, represent, and use the message digest to verify the contents of a zone for accuracy and completeness.  The ZONEMD Resource Record type is introduced for conveying the message digest data.</t></abstract>

